## Grouping

```ruby
# Group by column
Article.group(:status).count
# => {"draft"=>5, "published"=>10}

# Group with sum
Article.group(:category_id).sum(:views_count)
# => {1=>1000, 2=>500}

# Multiple groups
Article.group(:status, :category_id).count

# Having (filter grouped results)
Article.group(:user_id).having('COUNT(*) > 5')
```

